on his body.

19
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,420
It looks like
he was hacked to death with a long knife.

20
00:01:03,420 --> 00:01:06,020
My Lord, in my humble opinion,

21
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:08,580
