could be so good with a butcher knife?

25
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,160
I'll kill you!

26
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:18,780
I'll kill you!

27
00:01:19,050 --> 00:01:20,940
Just for this house!

28
