31
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,140
Yes, we can prove that!

32
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:28,700
-We can testify for Changyu!
-Last night,

33
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:30,620
-Changyu was at home!
-Yes!

34
00:01:30,620 --> 00:01:31,340
And we came here

35
00:01:31,340 --> 00:01:32,940
