77
00:05:45,330 --> 00:05:46,130
Mr. Wang,

78
00:05:47,650 --> 00:05:48,980
I didn't kill Uncle.

79
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,600
I know.

80
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:52,180
Changyu,

81
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,620
